able to communicate in the way in which she intends her words are a 
little...muffled...*

" Name? Uh...Ra..Rage. That what ...was called when...prisoner."

* She often had to pause in order to find the word in which she meant to 
speak, however, it was still a new thing to her that she had a voice other 
then the harsh roars she was normally used to.
Rage ran with Scourge towards a destination in which he was leading her, at 
least it got her away from all of those loud noises for a while.*
